defaultIs it desirable / feasible to separate cyclists from other road users, including prohibit
defaulting HGVs in peak hours …
defaultProhibiting HGVs in rush hour isn’t going to make a primary school child any safer on an ordinary urban or sub-urban road: she still has to interact with buses, vans and cars in our current environment.
